name: Graphic Design Precedent Collection
description:
A growing changing collection of graphic design precedents I reference in my work.


If you have any additions, please comment to let me know, or duplicate the file, add them in, and republish! I'll ty my best to append your additions to the original over time.


Update 2: Added Niklas Rosen


Update 1: Added Jessica Svednsen & Nordebrink Studio for typographic layout and simple form precedents respectively
